text: __NOTOC__ Location of Alexander County in Illinois This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Alexander County, Illinois. This is intended to be a complete list of the properties and districts on the National Register of Historic Places in Alexander County, Illinois, United States. Latitude and longitude coordinates are provided for many National Register properties and districts; these locations may be seen together in a map. There are 7 properties and districts listed on the National Register in the county. ==Current listings== |} ==See also== * List of National Historic Landmarks in Illinois * National Register of Historic Places listings in Illinois ==References== Alexander County *
